    "Name": "Coriolis IIC 1",
    "Details": "The Coriolis IIC is Clan Ice Hellion's 2888 rework of the original design, shedding 10 tons while adding considerably more punch through Clan technology. An Ultra AC/20 dominates close range while an LB-10X and Ultra AC/5 cover medium and longer engagements. Four ER Medium Lasers back up the ballistic suite and four jump jets give this 80-ton Clan machine the same rear-arc ambush capability that defined the original chassis.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - AC</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.18</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
